# Vendored third-party apps. We DO commit their source (so it ships "in the
# box"), but never their build artifacts or virtualenvs.
#
# SearXNG (see docs/searxng-managed-build-spec.md): clone into searxng/, record
# the pinned commit SHA in searxng/VERSION, then `rm -rf searxng/.git` so it's
# vendored files rather than an embedded gitlink.
searxng/.venv/
searxng/.git/
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc
**/*.pyo
